%p Hi #{@user.nickname},

%p
  Only
  = 25 - Date.today.day
  days left until Christmas!

%p We've got some suggested projects for you to send pull requests to this week.

%p
  - if @user.skills.any?
    We've guessed what languages you know based on the repos in your GitHub profile, if you'd like to change them, you can do that here: http://24pullrequests.com/email
  - else
    You can customise which types of project we suggest by setting your favourite languages in the preferences area here: http://24pullrequests.com/email

%h3 Suggested projects:

%ul
  - @suggested_projects.each do |project|
    %li
      %h4
        = project.name
        (#{project.main_language})
        = link_to project.github_url, project.github_url
      %p= project.description

%p Are you new to sending pull requests? Check out the guides here: http://24pullrequests.com/contributing

%p You can also follow @24pullrequests on twitter: http://twitter.com/24pullrequests

%p Unsubscribe or change frequency of these emails: http://24pullrequests.com/email

